## Gamification System

### XP Allocation
| Productivity Index | XP Earned |
|---|---|
| 90 – 100 | 1000 XP |
| 75 – 89 | 750 XP |
| 60 – 74 | 500 XP |
| Below 60 | 250 XP |

### Bonus XP
| Achievement | Bonus |
|---|---|
| 7-day attendance streak | +200 XP |
| Top 3 on leaderboard | +300 XP |
| Perfect manager rating week | +150 XP |

### Level Thresholds
| Level | Title | XP Required |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Rookie | 0 XP |
| 2 | Associate | 1,000 XP |
| 3 | Performer | 3,000 XP |
| 4 | Expert | 6,000 XP |
| 5 | Champion | 10,000 XP |

### Badges
| Badge | Trigger |
|---|---|
| 🎯 Target Crusher | 3 consecutive weeks above 90% target |
| 🪨 Rock Solid | Stability index above 85 for a month |
| 📈 On The Rise | Positive growth trend for 4 weeks straight |
| ✅ Never Miss | 100% attendance for 30 days |
| 🌅 Early Bird | On-time every day for 2 weeks |
| 📱 App Champion | Top app converter in department |
| ⭐ Fan Favourite | Avg manager rating above 4.5 for a month |

